{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A utility to sum 32 audio channels down to 2 (Raw Sum). Used by N2N to capture Monster Drums and other FX multi-out audio.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
