{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Filters MIDI output for the N2N Drum Arranger based on the REC CUE state. When REC CUE is off, filters out Channel 16. When REC CUE is on, filters out all channels except Channel 16.\par}
}

