{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 AHS Music Tech Repository\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A collection of effects and scripts primarily created for my students. Versions for public use will likely be released in the future.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 SCRIPTS\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Numbers2Notes - A Nashville Number System Chord Creation Tool\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Import and Export Chord Charts\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Create MIDI tracks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Print Chord Charts\sa180\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 There is a youtube video demonstrating an early version in action here:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b https://youtu.be/d9qhkUWvKKI?si=akMf5qpJ_tX5Myw2}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 \u9888 ?\u65039 ? Requirements & Setup\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Before using the script, please check the list of required extensions and plugins here:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u55357 ?\u56393 ? {\b {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://rockumk.github.io/AHS_Music_Tech/Numbers2Notes.html"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Numbers2Notes - View Details, Installation Guide & Requirements
}}}
}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab numbers2notes_spectrum - Creates a MIDI item containing the chord tones in all octaves.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 EFFECTS\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab N2N Drum Arranger - Drum sequencer tied into N2N song layout, groove, and swing.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab N2N Arp - Advanced arpeggiator with full knowledge of your song's chord mapping, cued to the N2N song layout, groove, and swing.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab MidiOnOff - Simple Effect to turn MIDI on and OFF via MIDI\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaCenterMIDIpitch - Recenters MIDI pitches around a user definable center pitch.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaPulse - A specialized version of RCJach's MIDI Note Beat Repeater effect.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Swing Track MIDI - Applies swing to even eights from 0 to 100% on individual MIDI tracks.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Swing Project MIDI - Applies swing to even eights from 0 to 100% across all tracks with the SwingTrackMIDI effect.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Wait-A-Moment - Sets a short delay compensation for MIDI arpeggiators.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Many more...\sa180\par}
}
